title: Dakota Johnson & Jamie Dornan Do Late Night Shows on Different Coasts!
text:
Tweet Dakota Johnson & Jamie Dornan Do Late Night Shows on Different Coasts! 
Dakota Johnson and Jamie Dornan are hard at work this week promoting their upcoming movie Fifty Shades Darker and both stars appeared on late night shows on Tuesday night (January 31)! 
Dakota made an appearance on The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon in New York City while Jamie stopped by Jimmy Kimmel Live in Hollywood. 
It appears that Dakota is going to do some sort of sketch in which Jimmy plays Christian Grey while she reprises her role as Anastasia Steele. 
Make sure to tune in for the shows tonight Just Jared on Facebook
